1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Little bunny, stop hiding.

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,000
It's you again, as expected.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:15,000
I've loved listening to your piano playing since I was little.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,000
So many years have passed.

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,000
You humans

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,000
age so quickly, don't you?

7
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Even if another ten thousand years pass, I will still look the same.

8
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:27,000
I've loved listening to you play the piano since I was a child.

9
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Even if ten thousand years pass, I will still feel the same.

10
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,000
But you, why do you come here every day?

11
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,000
What, are you trying to mess with my mind?

12
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Annoying.

13
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,000
I've already told you, I like you.

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
I've been practicing for many years, and I've sealed off my emotions long ago.

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,000
So, you better not waste your time.

16
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:49,000
I don't care, I want to be with you.

17
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Just because you say so?

18
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
What benefits can you bring me?

19
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,000
I... I...

20
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:58,000
I can protect you.

21
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
An unexpected guest has arrived.

22
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:05,000
Little rabbit, you better protect yourself first.

23
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Thanks, Dad.

24
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Lin Zhan, I've finally found you.

25
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,000
As long as I drink your blood,

26
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:18,000
I will soon greatly increase my power and achieve immortality!

